    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Faith Community was created with a simple but powerful purpose: to provide a safe, encouraging space 
      where believers can share their testimonies, struggles, victories, and spiritual insights with one another.
    </p>
    <p>
      We believe that every faith journey is unique and valuable. Whether you're sharing a powerful testimony, 
      asking for prayer, seeking guidance, or simply reflecting on scripture, your voice matters here.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Believe</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Community matters.</strong> We are stronger together than apart.</li>
      <li><strong>Every story has value.</strong> Your experience can encourage someone else.</li>
      <li><strong>Grace and love.</strong> We treat everyone with respect and compassion.</li>
      <li><strong>Growth is a journey.</strong> We're all works in progress, and that's okay.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Rooms</h2>
    <p>
      We've organized our community into themed rooms to help you find the right space for your sharing:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Share Your Experience</strong> - General testimonies and stories</li>
      <li><strong>Overcoming Struggles</strong> - Victory stories and encouragement</li>
      <li><strong>Prayer Requests</strong> - Community prayer support</li>
      <li><strong>Past Struggles</strong> - Healing and reflection</li>
      <li><strong>Faith Journey</strong> - Personal growth stories</li>
      <li><strong>Scripture Reflections</strong> - Biblical insights and devotionals</li>
      <li><strong>Questions & Guidance</strong> - Seeking spiritual advice</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you're looking to share your story, find encouragement, or simply connect with fellow believers, 
      we welcome you to our community. <%= link_to "Create an account", new_user_registration_path %> 
      today and begin your journey with us.
    </p>

